Hello neighbors,

Spring is here, and we’re excited to invite you to our annual Spring Community Potluck!

Date: Saturday, May 4, 2024
Time: 11:30 AM – 2:30 PM
Location: Maple Street Community Center, Hall B

What to bring:
- A homemade dish or dessert to share
- Serving utensils for your item
- A labeled card with ingredients (for allergies)
- Your own reusable plate and cutlery, if possible

We’ll provide:
- Beverages (water, iced tea, lemonade)
- Tables and chairs
- Music and games for all ages

Please reply to this email by April 28th to let us know:
1. The number of people attending from your household.
2. The dish you plan to bring.

Feel free to drop by early if you’d like to help with setup. We appreciate any extra hands between 9:30 AM and 11:00 AM.

If you have questions or need assistance, contact us at community@local.org or call (555) 123-4567.

Looking forward to good food and great company!

Warm regards,
The Community Potluck Committee